// ã‚µãƒ¼ãƒ“ã‚¹ã”ã¨ã®æœ€é©ãƒ—ãƒ­ã‚¸ã‚§ã‚¯ãƒˆé¸æŠé–¢æ•°
function selectBestProject(serviceName, quotas) {
  const serviceQuotas = quotas.filter(q => q.service_name === serviceName && q.remaining > 0);
  if (serviceQuotas.length === 0) return null;

  // æ®‹ã‚Šã‚¯ã‚©ãƒ¼ã‚¿ãŒæœ€ã‚‚å¤šã„ãƒ—ãƒ­ã‚¸ã‚§ã‚¯ãƒˆã‚’é¸æŠ
  serviceQuotas.sort((a, b) => b.remaining - a.remaining);
  return {
    project_id: serviceQuotas[0].project_id,
    remaining: serviceQuotas[0].remaining,
    quota_limit: serviceQuotas[0].quota_limit
  };
}

// å„ã‚µãƒ¼ãƒ“ã‚¹ã®æœ€é©ãƒ—ãƒ­ã‚¸ã‚§ã‚¯ãƒˆ
const optimalProjects = {
  youtube: selectBestProject('youtube', quotas),
  gemini: selectBestProject('gemini', quotas),
  elevenlabs: selectBestProject('elevenlabs', quotas),
  openai: selectBestProject('openai', quotas),
  anthropic: selectBestProject('anthropic', quotas)
};

const results = [];

for (const channel of channels) {
  const apiCost = channel.api_cost_total || 1;
  const revenue = channel.revenue_generated || 0;
  const roiScore = revenue / apiCost;

  let matchedRule = rules.find(r => r.rule_name === 'Dãƒ©ãƒ³ã‚¯ï¼ˆæ–°è¦ãƒ»æœªè©•ä¾¡ï¼‰');

  for (const rule of rules) {
    const meetsRoi = rule.min_roi_score === null || roiScore >= rule.min_roi_score;
    const meetsRetention = rule.min_retention_rate === null || channel.avg_retention >= rule.min_retention_rate;
    const meetsImpressions = rule.min_impressions === null || channel.total_views >= rule.min_impressions;

    if (meetsRoi && meetsRetention && meetsImpressions) {
      matchedRule = rule;
      break;
    }
  }

  const newRank = matchedRule?.rule_name?.match(/([SABCD])ãƒ©ãƒ³ã‚¯/)?.[1] || 'D';
  const rankChanged = newRank !== channel.current_rank;

  // TTS/Image tierã«åŸºã¥ãå‹•çš„APIã‚­ãƒ¼é¸æŠ
  const ttsTier = matchedRule?.tts_tier || 'openai_tts';
  const imageTier = matchedRule?.image_tier || 'dalle';

  let selectedTtsProject = null;
  let selectedImageProject = null;

  if (ttsTier === 'elevenlabs') {
    selectedTtsProject = optimalProjects.elevenlabs;
  } else {
    selectedTtsProject = optimalProjects.openai;
  }

  if (imageTier === 'midjourney') {
    selectedImageProject = optimalProjects.openai; // MJã¯DiscordçµŒç”±
  } else {
    selectedImageProject = optimalProjects.openai;
  }

  results.push({
    channel_id: channel.channel_id,
    channel_name: channel.channel_name,
    video_count: channel.video_count,
    total_views: channel.total_views,
    avg_retention: channel.avg_retention,
    avg_ctr: channel.avg_ctr,
    roi_score: roiScore.toFixed(4),
    previous_rank: channel.current_rank,
    new_rank: newRank,
    rank_changed: rankChanged,
    assigned_tts_tier: ttsTier,
    assigned_image_tier: imageTier,
    budget_multiplier: matchedRule?.monthly_budget_multiplier || 1.0,
    dynamic_api_keys: {
      tts_project: selectedTtsProject?.project_id || 'default',
      tts_remaining_quota: selectedTtsProject?.remaining || 0,
      image_project: selectedImageProject?.project_id || 'default',
      image_remaining_quota: selectedImageProject?.remaining || 0,
      youtube_project: optimalProjects.youtube?.project_id || 'default',
      gemini_project: optimalProjects.gemini?.project_id || 'default'
    }
  });
}

// ã‚¯ã‚©ãƒ¼ã‚¿ãƒªã‚»ãƒƒãƒˆå¯¾è±¡ã®æ›´æ–°
const resetTargets = quotas.filter(q => q.needs_reset).map(q => ({
  project_id: q.project_id,
  service_name: q.service_name
}));

return results.map(r => ({ json: { ...r, quota_reset_needed: resetTargets } }));

const items = $input.all().map(item => item.json);
const channelItems = items.filter(i => i.channel_id);
const rankChanges = channelItems.filter(i => i.rank_changed);

const summary = {
